quran[200]{c,v,t}:
  3,1,"Alm."
  3,2,"Öebbi, ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa, Amuddir, Imezgi."
  3,3,"Issers ak d Tazmamt s tidep, d atebbet n wayen ip id izwaren. Issers ed Tuôa akked Linoil,"
  3,4,"uqbel, d nnhaya i medden. Issers ed Leqwôan. Ih, wid inekôen issekniyen n Öebbi, fellasen aâaqeb uqûiê. Öebbi d Uzmir, Ippara d ppaô."
  3,5,"Ih, Öebbi ur aS iffir wacemma di tmurt, ne$ deg igenni."
  3,6,"D Neppa i wen Ippaken udem, di tâabbav, akken i S ihwa. Ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa, Uzmir, Bab n ûûwab."
  3,7,"Neppa i k ed Issersen Tazmamt, degs issekniyen uvhiôen, nitni d tayimmap n Tezmamt. Wiyav d licwaô. D$a, wid iwumi mmalen wulawen, teddun akked wayen illan d licwaô, ssaramen ahewwel, ssaramen asefhem is. I Issnen asefhem is, siwa Öebbi. Qqaôen imawlan n tmusni: ""numen yis. S$uô Mass nne$ akw"". Id ismektayen, siwa uâqilen."
  3,8,"A Mass nne$! Ur Smili ulawen nne$, mbaâd ma Tenhiv a$. Efk a$ d, s$uôeK, aêunu. Ih, Keçç, ard Am$it."
  3,9,"A Mass nne$! Keçç, s tidep, ara Ijemmlen medden, ass i$ef ur illi ccekk. S tidep, Öebbi ur Izeggel lemâahda."
  3,10,"Ih, wid ijehlen, ur sen d ippawi acemma, ar Öebbi, wayla nnsen, ne$ tarwa nnsen. Widak, d nitni ay d isufa n tmes."
  3,11,"D tin n ugdud n Ferâun akked wid i ten id izwaren. Skaddben issekniyen nne£. Iwwet iten Öebbi, ilmend ibekkaven nnsen. Öebbi Iwâaô i uâaqeb."
  3,12,"Ini i wid ijehlen: ""a ppepwa$elbem, a ppepwafesrem di Loahennama"". A yir usu!"
  3,13,"Ni$ d assekni, i kunwi, mi mlalent snat trebbuyaâ. Yiwet tepna$ deg ubrid n Öebbi; tayev d tajehlit, twala d snat, s yiéôi s. Öebbi Ippak afus, s tallalt iS, i win i S ihwan. Deg wayagi, s tidep, aselmed i wid ipwalin."
  3,14,"D tucbiêt ay d tedheô i yimdanen leêmala n ccehwiyyat: tilawin, tarwa, iâammuôen ibararen n ddheb akked lfeîîa, iâawdiwen n ccetla, lmal, akal. Ayagi, d zzhu n tmeddurt n ddunit. Öebbi, $uôeS amkan lâali, n tu$alin."
  3,15,"Ini: ""ad awen mle$ i yifen aya? I wid ipêezziben, ar Mass nnsen, leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, degsen ad wekkôen, tilawin iûfan, akked llza s$uô Öebbi"". Öebbi Ipwali imdanen;"
  3,16,"wid iqqaôen: ""a Mass nne$! Nekwni, s tidep, numen. Ihi, Semmeê a$ ibekkaven nne$, Sellek a$ seg uâaqeb n tmes""."
  3,17,"Iûebôiyen, imawlan n tidep, imvuâen, wid ipseddiqen, wid iste$fiôen di tafrara."
  3,18,"Icuhhed Öebbi ar ur illi ôebbi, siwa Neppa. Akken lmalayek, akked imawlan n tmusni. Ibedd i lmizan. Ur illi ôebbi, siwa Neppa, Uzmir, Bab n ûûwab."
  3,19,"Ih, ddin ar Öebbi d annuz. Ur mgarraden wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt, armi deffir n tisin n tussna $uôsen, wa iqheô wa. Wid inekôen issekniyen n Öebbi, ihi, Öebbi Ip$awal deg uqeîîi."
  3,20,"Ma nuqmen k, ini: ""unze$ aS i Öebbi. Akken, wid iddan yidi. Ini i wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt, akked at war tussna: ""ma tunzem""? Ma unzen, ihi, pwanhan. Ma wexxôen, ay fellak siwa anabi. Öebbi Ipwali imdanen."
  3,21,"Ih, wid inekôen issekniyen n Öebbi, u pna$en lambiyya, war ssebba, u pna$en wid seg yimdanen ippamôen lmizan, becceô iten s uâaqeb aqeôêan."
  3,22,"Widak, d wid iwumi mêan igiten nnsen di ddunit, di laxert. Ur sâin isellaken."
  3,23,"Day ur twalav ara wid iwumi ippunefk kra si Tezmamt, la ssuturen, i Tezmamt n Öebbi, aêuddu garasen? Sinna, ad iwexxeô urbaâ segsen, u nitni pnamaren."
  3,24,"Ayagi, acku nnan: ""ur a$ teppep tmes, siwa kra n wussan"". I$uôô iten, di ddin nnsen, wayen id snulfuyen."
  3,25,"Amek ihi, ma Njemmel iten, ass ideg, ur degs ccekk, yal yiwen ad i$ellet ayen ikseb, nitni ur ppudensen."
  3,26,"Ini: ""a Öebbi, Agellid n tgelda, Teppakev tagelda i win i K ihwan, Teppeksev tagelda i win i K ihwan, Tepâuzzuv win i K ihwan, Tesdulluv win i K ihwan. Lxiô deg ufus i K. Ih, Keçç, Tzemrev i yal cci."
  3,27,"Tessekcamev iv deg wass. Tessekcamev ass deg iv. Tessuffu$ev amuddir si lmegget. Tessuffu$ev lmegget seg umuddir. Tep$itiv win i K ihwan, war aktili""."
  3,28,"Lmumnin ur pparan ijehliyen d iêbiben nnsen, war lmumnin. Win ixedmen aya, ur illi, s wacemma, ar Öebbi. Kkes ed aêezzeb i têezzbem iman nnwen segsen. Iâaggen awen Öebbi s yiman iS. Tu$alin ar Öebbi."
  3,29,"Ini: ""ama teffrem i illan deg idmaren nnwen, ne$ tessnaâtem t, Öebbi Iéôa t"". Iéôa i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt. Öebbi Izmer i yal cci."
  3,30,"Ass ideg yal iman ad iaf irs ed, wayen ixdem n lxiô, akked wayen ixdem n cceôô, ad issirem a ppili, garas yides, tallit $ezzifen! Iâaggen awen Öebbi, af yiman iS. Öebbi d Umâin ar imdanen."
  3,31,"Ini: ""ma têemmlem Öebbi, ddut yidi. A kwen Iâuzz Öebbi, ad awen Isemmeê ibekkaven nnwen. Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu""."
  3,32,"Ini: ""ssemêesset i Öebbi akked Umazan"". Ma wexxôen, ihi Öebbi ur Iêemmel ara ijehliyen."
  3,33,"Ih, Öebbi Ismenyaf, i imavalen, Adem, Nuê, tawacult n Ibôahim, tawacult n Âimôan."
  3,34,"Wa iurew wa. Öebbi Issel, d Amusnaw."
  3,35,"Mi tenna tmeîîut n Âimôan: ""a Mass iw! Wekkle$ aK ayen illan di tâabbuî iw, d lewkala, Eqbel s$uôi. Keçç, ih, d win Isellen, d Amusnaw""."
  3,36,"Mi p id turew, tenna: ""a Mass iw! Urwe$ p id d nnta"". - Öebbi Iéôa, sennig akw, d acu d turew. Ddkeô, maççi am nnta. - ""Nek semma$ as Meryem, rri$ p seddaw tecvaî iK, neppat akked tarwa s, mgal Cciîan imenfi""."
  3,37,"Iôêeb yis Mass is, asteôêeb ilhan; Isgem ip, tigmi ilhan; Ikwellef ip i Zakariyya. Yal tikelt ara iôuê $uôes Zakariyya ar lmiêreb, a n iaf tesâa ôôeéq. Inna: ""a Meryem! Ansi i m d ikka waya""? Tenna: ""s$uô Öebbi. Öebbi, s tidep, Iôeééeq win i S ihwan, war aktili""."
  3,38,"D$a Zakariyya inuj $uô Mass is, inna: ""a Mass iw! Efk iyi d, s$uôeK, tarwa ifazen. Keçç, s tidep, Tsellev i unuju""."
  3,39,"Mi ibedd, ipéalla di lmeêreb, ssawlent as d lmalayek: ""Ibecceô ik Öebbi s Yaêia, d atebbet n wawal n Öebbi, d ssid, d azedgan, d nnbi, seg iâaôviyen""."
  3,40,"Inna: ""a Mass iw! Amek ara sâu$ aqcic? Ni$ wessre$, tameîîut iw d tiâiqeôt"". Inna: ""akka, Öebbi Ixeddem ayen i S ihwan""."
  3,41,"Inna: ""a Mass iw! Efk iyi d assekni"". Inna: ""assekni ik, ur tepmeslayev i medden krav wussan. As$al kan. Mmekti d aîas Mass ik, sbuccaâ iT tameddit, tafrara""."
  3,42,"Mi s nnant lmalayek: ""a Meryem! Öebbi, s tidep, Ifren ikem, Izzazdeg ikem, Ismenyaf ikem i tlawin imavalen."
  3,43,"A Meryem! Anez i Mass im, knu yaS, îîinez akked wid iîîinizen""."
  3,44,"Ayagi si tmucuha i iffren, Nweêêa yak t. Ur telliv yidsen, mi jebden taseqqaôt, anwa segsen ara itkelfen $ef Meryem. Ur telliv yidsen mi mqellaâen."
  3,45,"Mi s nnant lmalayek: ""a Meryem! Öebbi, s tidep, Ibecceô ikem s wawal s$uôeS, ism is: lmasiê Âisa, mmi s n Meryem; mucaâ di ddunit akked laxert; seg iqôiben."
  3,46,"A d ipmeslay i medden, si dduê, am unqaqôi, ad yili seg iâaôviyen""."
  3,47,"Tenna: ""a Mass iw! Amek ara sâu$ aqcic, ur iyi innul urgaz""? Inna: ""akka. Öebbi Ixelleq ayen i S ihwan. Ma Iseyya lameô, ad as Yini kan: ""ili""! Ad yili""."
  3,48,"Ad as Isselmed Tazmamt, ûûwab, Tuôa, Linoil."
  3,49,"D amazan ar At Isôail: ""ni$ nek usi$ d, $uôwen, s issekniyen s$uô Mass nnwen. Nek ad awen d xelqe$, s talaxt, ayen icban afôux, ad ûuve$ degs, ad iu$al d afôux, ma Ib$a Öebbi. Ad sseêlu$ ader$al, amuvin n lbeôû, a d ssidre$ lmeggtin, ma Ib$a Öebbi. Ad awen ini$ d acu teppeppem, akked wayen txezznem deg ixxamen nnwen. Deg waya, s tidep, d assekni i kunwi, ma d lmumnin ay tellam."
  3,50,"A d tebbte$ iyi d izwaren di Tuôa, ad awen êelle$ kra n wayen illan ipwagdel awen. Usi$ d, $uôwen, s ussekni, s$uô Mass nnwen. Ëezbet i Öebbi, a$et iyi awal."
  3,51,"Öebbi, s tidep, d Mass iw, u d Mass nnwen. Ihi, âabdet eP, d wagi ay d abrid uwqim""."
  3,52,"Mi israê Âisa tijehli s$uôsen, inna: ""anwi ay d imâiwnen iw ar Öebbi""? Nnan as d lexwan: ""nekwni d imâiwnen n Öebbi. Numen s Öebbi, eched ar nekwni d imvuâen."
  3,53,"A Mass nne$! Numen s wayen id Tessersev, nedda d umazan, Aru ya$ seg inagan""."
  3,54,"Undin. Iundi Öebbi. Öebbi Yif akw imendayen."
  3,55,"Mi s Inna Öebbi: ""a Âisa! Nek ad Ddme$ ôôuê ik, a k id Ssali$ $uôI, a k id Ssiferre$ seg wid ijehlen, ad Rre$, wid iddan yidek, sennig wid ijehlen, ar ass n tnekra"". Sinna, tu$alin nnwen $uôI, ad Ëudde$, garawen, $ef wayen i$ef teppemgarradem."
  3,56,"Ma d wid ijehlen, a ten Âaqbe$ di ddunit, di laxert, aâaqeb aqeûêan. Ur asen ppilin isellaken."
  3,57,"Wanag wid iumnen u xeddmen ayen ilhan, ad asen Ifk arrazen nnsen. Öebbi ur Iêemmel ara imednas."
  3,58,"Ayagi i ak Nemmal seg issekniyen, akked usmekti uûwib."
  3,59,"Ih, amedya n Âisa, ar Öebbi, am umedya n Adem. Ixelq it seg wakal, sinna, Inna yas: ""ili""! Illa."
  3,60,"Tidep, s$uô Mass ik. Ur ppili seg wid ipcukkun."
  3,61,"I win i k inumren fellas, deffir wayen i k id iusan n tussna, ini: ""yyaw a nenced tarwa nne$, tarwa nnwen, tilawin nne$, tilawin nnwen, iman nne$, iman nnwen. Sinna, a nemmesgill, a nd²âu ad Ixzu Öebbi ikeddaben."
  3,62,"Ih, tagi d tamacahup n tidep, ur illi ôebbi siwa Öebbi. Ih, Öebbi, Neppa, war ccekk, d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab."
  3,63,"Ma wexxren, ihi Öebbi Issen ifessaden."
  3,64,"Ini: ""a yAt Tezmamt! Yyaw ar wawal azduklan garane$ yidwen. A naâbed siwa Öebbi, ur aS nepcarak acemma; ur pparan, kra segne$ kra, d iôebbiten, war Öebbi"". Ma wexxôen, init: ""cehhdet ar nekwni d imvuâen""."
  3,65,"A yAt Tezmamt! Acimi temnamarem $ef Ibôahim? Ur n risent Tuôa akked Linoil, armi deffir es, day ur tmeyyzem ara?"
  3,66,"Kunwi, atan temnamarem $ef wayen tessnem. Ihi, acimi temnamarem $ef wayen ur tessinem? Öebbi Issen, kunwi ur tessinem."
  3,67,"Ur illi Ibôahim d uday ne$ d amasiêi, maca illa d amvuâ imalen ar tidep. Ur illi seg imcurak."
  3,68,"Ih, imdanen iqeôben nezzeh ar Ibôahim, war ccekk, d wid i t ivefôen, akked Nnbi agi, akked wid iumnen. Öebbi d Bab n lmumnin."
  3,69,"Arbaâ, seg At Tezmamt, ib$a a kwen itlef. Ara telfen siwa iman nnsen, ur éôin."
  3,70,"A yAt Tezmamt! Acimi tugim issekniyen n Öebbi, u kunwi tepwalim?"
  3,71,"A yAt Tezmamt! Acimi teslusum, i tidep, ayen idensen, u teppeffrem tidep, kunwi teêûam?"
  3,72,"Arbaâ, seg At Tezmamt, inna: ""amnet mi iuli wass, s wayen id irsen ar wid iumnen, nekôet tameddit"". Amendeô ma a d u$alen."
  3,73,"Ppamnet kan win ivefôen ddin nnwen. Ini: ""ih, nnhaya d nnhaya n Öebbi. A ppeppunefk i yiwen am wayen i wen ippunefken"". Ne$ a kwen namren af Mass nnwen. Ini: ""lfevl, s tidep, deg ufus n Öebbi, Ippak it i win i S ihwan"". Öebbi d Ajemmal, d Amusnaw."
  3,74,"Iâateq aêunu S i win i S ihwan. Öebbi d Bab n lfevl ameqwôaêan."
  3,75,"Seg wAt Tezmamt, illa win, xas teooiv as adrim aîas, ad ak t id irr. Illa wayev segsen, ma teooiv as adinar, ur ak t id ippara, alamma tezgiv $uôes. Akka, acku nitni nnan: ""ur a$ d ppawven at war tussna"". U ggaren d tikerkas $ef Öebbi, u nitni éôan."
  3,76,"Xaîi! Win iîîfen di lemâahda s, u iêezzeb…ihi, Öebbi Iêemmel wid ipêezziben."
  3,77,"Ih, wid ippa$en s lemâahda n Öebbi akked tgallit nnsen, ayen ôxisen, widak, ur ppawin amur di laxert, ur asen Ipmeslay Öebbi, ur ten id Ipmuqul, ass n tnekra, ur ten Izzizdig. Fellasen aâaqeb aqeôêan."
  3,78,"Ih, arbaâ segsen ssexsaôen Tazmamt s yilsawen nnsen, iwakken a p$ilem n Tezmamt, ayen ur nelli n Tezmamt. Qqaôen: ""aya s$uô Öebbi"", u neppa ur illi s$uô Öebbi. U qqaren tikerkas $ef Öebbi, u nitni éôan."
  3,79,"Ur ippunefk ara i umdan iwumi Ifka Öebbi Tazmamt, ûûwab, u Irra t d nnbi, ad iu$al ad yini i medden: ""ilit d imdanen iw, war Öebbi"". Maca: ""ilit d iselmaden, imi tesselmadem Tazmamt, u tlemdem""."
  3,80,"Ur awen Iumeô ara a pperrem lmalayek akked lambiyya, d imawlan. Day awen Iameô tijehli, mbaâd ma tellam d imvuâen?"
  3,81,"Mi Iîîef Öebbi laâqed n lambiyya: ""s tidep, Fki$ awen si Tezmamt akw si ûûwab, sinna, iusa kwen id umazan, i itebbten ayen illan $uôwen. Amnet yis, âiwnet ep"". Inna: ""tâazmem u tqeblem, f waya, laâqed iW""? Nnan as: ""naâzem"". Inna: ""ihi, cehhdet, Nek, yidwen, seg inagan""."
  3,82,"Wid iwexxôen, deffir waya, nitni d iballa$en."
  3,83,"Day b$an ddin ur nelli n Öebbi? U Neppa, unzen aS i illan di tmurt akked igenwan, b$an ne$ ugin. £uôeS, tu$alin nnsen."
  3,84,"Ini: ""numen s Öebbi, akked wayen id irsen $uône$, akked wayen id irsen ar Ibôahim, Ismaâil, Isêaq, Iaâqub, laâôac, ayen ippunefken i Musa, Âisa, akked lambiyya, s$uô Mass nnsen. Ur nesmenyaf yiwen degsen. Nekwni nunez aS""."
  3,85,"Win ib$an ddin, war annuz, ur ipwaqbal s$uôes. U neppa, di laxert, seg imexsuôen."
  3,86,"Amek ara Inhu Öebbi agdud inekôen deffir liman is, u cehhden ar Amazan d tidep, u iusa ten id ubeggen? Öebbi ur Inehhu agdud imednas."
  3,87,"Widak, aqeîîi nnsen d ddell s$uô Öebbi, d lmalayek, akked imdanen meôôa."
  3,88,"Degs ad wekkôen; ur ippifsus fellasen uâaqeb, ur stiseren."
  3,89,"Kkes ed wid iu$alen nedmen, deffir waya, u xedmen ayen ilhan. Ih, Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu."
  3,90,"Ih, wid ijehlen, deffir liman nnsen, sinna, rnan di tijehli, ur tepwaqbal nndama nnsen. Widak d im$eôôqen."
  3,91,"Ih, wid ijehlen, u mmuten d ijehliyen, ur ipwaqbal s$uô yiwen degsen, azal n tmurt n ddheb, a t id ifdu. I widak, aâaqeb aqeôêan, ur sâin amâiwen."
  3,92,"Ur teppawvem ar ppuba, d awez$i, alamma tseddqem seg wayen têemmlem. Kra n wayen tseddqem n cci, ihi, Öebbi Iéôa t."
  3,93,"Yal lqut illa iêell i At Isôail, siwa ayen igdel Isôail i iman is, uqbel a d ters Tuôa. Ini: ""awit ed Tuôa, $eôt ep, ma tessawalem tidep""."
  3,94,"Wid id igren tikerkas $ef Öebbi, deffir waya, nitni d imednas."
  3,95,"Ini: ""Inna d Öebbi tidep; ddut d ddin n Ibôahim, i imalen ar tidep, ur nelli seg imcurak""."
  3,96,"Ih, axxam amezwaru, i irsen i medden, war ccekk, d win n Bekka. Iôqa, d nnhaya i imavalen."
  3,97,"Degs issekniyen iberrzen; d axxam n Ibôahim. Win it ikecmen, atan di laman. I Öebbi, iwata ad êuoen medden s Axxam, ma zemren a t awven. Win iugin, ihi, Rebbi ur Iêwao ara imavalen."
  3,98,"Ini: ""a yAt Tezmamt! Acimi tnekôem issekniyen n Öebbi""? Öebbi d Anagi n wayen txeddmem."
  3,99,"Ini: ""a yAt Tezmamt! Acimi teîîeôôifem, wid iumnen, seg ubrid n Öebbi? Tessaramem t iaâwej, u kunwi d inagan"". Ur I$fil Öebbi $ef wayen txeddmem."
  3,100,"A wid iumnen! Ma tu$em awal i urbaâ, seg wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt, a kwen rren d ijehliyen, deffir liman nnwen."
  3,101,"Amek tnekôem, u kunwi $ôan awen d issekniyen n Öebbi, u, garawen, Amazan iS? Win iîîfen di Öebbi, ni$ ipwanha s abrid uwqim."
  3,102,"A wid iumnen! Ëezzbet i Öebbi, akken Iklal aêezzeb. Ur ppemmtet alamma tunzem."
  3,103,"Eîfet akw di teêmilt n Öebbi, ur ppemfaôaqet. Mmektit ed ayen ikwen I$at Öebbi. Mi tellam d icenga, Issemlal ulawen nnwen. S l$it iS, tu$alem d atmaten. Tellam $ef rrif n maylellif n tmes, Isellek ikwen segs. Akka i wen Ipbeggin Öebbi issekniyen iS, amendeô ma a ppepwanhum."
  3,104,"Amar ad yili, segwen, lois i ineccden ar lxiô, ippamôen lqanun, itekksen ayen n dir. Widak d imerbaê."
  3,105,"Ur ppilit am wid imfaôaqen, u mgarraden, deffir n tisin ubeggen $uôsen. I widak, aâaqeb aqeôêan,"
  3,106,"ass ideg ara imlulen wudmawen, ara ibriken wudmawen. Wanag wid iwumi ara ibriken wudmawen nnsen: ""tnekôem, deffir liman nnwen? Jeôôbet aâaqeb, ilmend n wayen tnekôem""."
  3,107,"Wanag wid iwumi ara a imlulen wudmawen nnsen, ad ilin deg uêunu n Öebbi. Nitni, degs, ad wekkôen."
  3,108,"D wigi ay d issekniyen n Öebbi. Neqqaô ak ten id, s tidep. Ur Ib$i Öebbi ddens i imavalen."
  3,109,"N Öebbi i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt. Ar Öebbi tu$alin n lumuô."
  3,110,"Tifem akw leoyus id iff$en i medden. Teppamôem lqanun, teppekksem ayen n dir, tumnem s Öebbi. Ppif, i At Tezmamt, lemmer uminen. Garasen lmumnin; tegwti degsen d iballa$en."
  3,111,"Cwiî kan ara kwen vuôôen. Ma nnu$en kwen, ad rewlen, sinna, ur sâun amâiwen."
  3,112,"Iwwet iten ddell anda ma llan, siwa wid iîîfen di teêmilt n Öebbi, u di teêmilt n medden. Lqan urrif n Öebbi, u te$li d tiggulelt fellasen. Ayagi, acku llan nekôen issekniyen n Öebbi, la neqqen lambiyya, war ssebba. Ayagi, imi âuûan u zgaren tilas."
  3,113,"Ur aâdilen. Illa lois, seg At Tezmamt, i iqqaôen issekniyen n Öebbi deg iv, u nitni kennun."
  3,114,"Umnen s Öebbi akked wass aneggaru, ppamôen lqanun, tekksen ayen n dir, pêirin ar lxiô. Widak seg iâaôviyen."
  3,115,"Ayen xedmen n lxiô, ur asen ipwankaô. Öebbi Issen wid ipêezziben."
  3,116,"Ih, wid ijehlen, ur asen d ippawi acemma, ar Öebbi, wayla nnsen, ne$ tarwa nnsen. Widak d at tmes, degs ad wekkôen."
  3,117,"Amedya n wayen pseôôifen di tmeddurt n ddunit agi, am umedya n wavu, degs abruri. Iêuza iger n ugdud idensen iman is. Isnegr it. Ur ten Idnis Öebbi; d iman nnsen ay dennisen."
  3,118,"A wid iumnen! Ur pparat d iêbiben, wur nelli segwen. Ur zgalen a kwen hewwlen. B$an a kwen hejjnen. Ni$ ibda d lbwe$v seg imawen nnsen. Ayen iffren deg ulawen nnsen, i$elb it. Ni$ Nbeggen awen ed issekniyen, ma tepmeyyizem."
  3,119,"Atan kunwi d wid i ten iêemmlen, ur kwen êemmlen. Tumnem di Tezmamt, s lekmal is. Ma mmugren kwen, ad inin: ""numen"". Mi $aben, ad $eééen ivudan nnsen si zzâaf fellawen. Ini: ""emmtet si zzâaf nnwen""! Ih, Öebbi Iéôa i illan deg idmaren."
  3,120,"Ma iusa kwen id ise$, a ten isnu$ben. Ma tevôa yidwen tucmip, ad feôêen yis. Ma tûebôem, u têezbem, ur kwen teîîuôôu s wacemma, tandit nnsen. Ni$ Izzi Öebbi i wayen xeddmen."
  3,121,"Mi teff$ev, ûûbeê zik, si twacult ik, temmalev i lmumnin imukan umennu$, Öebbi Issel, d Amusnaw."
  3,122,"Mi qôib feclent snat n trebbuyaâ nnwen, u Öebbi d Bab nnsent. Iwata i yal lmumen, ad ippkel $ef Öebbi."
  3,123,"Ni$ Iâiwen ikwen Öebbi di Badô, mi tellam tendellem. Ihi, êezzbet i Öebbi, amar a ppesnemmrem."
  3,124,"Mi tenniv i lmumnin: ""day ur testeqnaâm ara, mi kwen Iâiwen Öebbi s krav igima n lmalayek, id irsen""?"
  3,125,"Xaîi, ma tûebôem u têezzbem, ma $ewwsen d fellawen, a kwen Iâiwen Mass nnwen, s smus igima n lmalayek ikkaten."
  3,126,"Ur Iga akka Öebbi, siwa i ubecceô nnwen, ad rtiêen yis wulawen nnwen. Rrbeê s$uô Öebbi kan, Uzmir, Bab n ûûwab."
  3,127,"Iwakken ad Iôé arbaâ n wid ijehlen, ne$ a ten Iééaâ, ad u$alen nne$wnin."
  3,128,"Ur k iaâna lameô s wacemma. Ad asen Issuref, ne$ a ten Iâaqeb, nitni d imednas."
  3,129,"N Öebbi i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt. Ipsemmiê i win i S ihwan. Ipâaqab win i S ihwan. Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu."
  3,130,"A wid iumnen! Ur teppet rrba ipzeggiden, tepzeggid. Ëezzbet i Öebbi, amar a prebêem."
  3,131,"Ëezzbet ilmend n tmes i ippuheggan i ijehliyen."
  3,132,"A$et awal i Öebbi akked Umazan, amar ad yili uêunu fellawen."
  3,133,"£iwlet ar ssmaê s$uô Mass nnwen, akked Loennet iwsâan am tmurt akked igenwan. Teppuhegga d i wid ipêezziben,"
  3,134,"wid ipseddiqen - sâan ne$ xuûûen -, wid isnusun reffu, wid ipsemmiêen i medden - Öebbi Iêemmel lâuûam -,"
  3,135,"wid, ma xedmen tucmip, ne$ densen iman nnsen, a d mmektin Öebbi, ad ste$fôen $ef ibekkaven nnsen. Anwa Ipsemmiêen ibekkaven siwa Öebbi? Ur pgerninen deg wayen xedmen, u nitni éôan."
  3,136,"Widak, akafi nnsen d ssmaê n Mass nnsen, akked leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, degsen ad wekkôen. D arraz igerzen i wid issewqamen."
  3,137,"Âaddant tedyanin uqbel nnwen. Iniget di tmurt, walit amek tevôa d wid id iggaren tikerkas."
  3,138,"Wagi d abeggen i medden, d nnhaya akked unecced i wid ipêezziben."
  3,139,"Ur ppifcilet, ur $webnet, d kunwi i iaâlayen, ma d lmumnin ay tellam."
  3,140,"Ma iêuza kwen lada, ni$ lada i t icban iêuza agdud. Ussan agi Nerra ten, ger medden, d tidwal, iwakken ad Yissin Öebbi wid iumnen, ad Iddem segwen inagan. Öebbi ur Iêemmel ara imednas."
  3,141,"Iwakken ad Ijeôôeb Öebbi wid iumnen, u ad Isqucc ijehliyen."
  3,142,"Day t$ilem a pkecmem Loennet, wanag ur Iéôi ara Öebbi wid ijuhden segwen, ur Issin ara iûebôiyen?"
  3,143,"Ni$ tepmennim tameppant, uqbel a p id temmagrem. Ni$ twalam p, kunwi tepmuqulem."
  3,144,"Muêemmed d Amazan kan. Ni$ âaddan imazanen, uqbel is. Ma immut ne$ ipwan$a, day a ppu$alem ar deffir? Win ara iu$alen ar deffir, ur iîîuôôu Öebbi s wacemma. Öebbi ad Ikafi wid isnemmiren."
  3,145,"Ur ipmeppat umdan siwa ma Irad Öebbi, di lajel iuran. Win ib$an akafi n ddunit, ad as t Nefk. Win ib$an akafi n laxeôt, ad as t Nefk. A Nkafi wid isnemmiren."
  3,146,"Acêal n lambiyya i innu$en, idda yidsen urbaâ iqwan, ur fcilen seg wayen iten issaâtben, deg ubrid n Öebbi, ur xuzen, ur fkin mayna. Öebbi Iêemmel iûebôiyen."
  3,147,"Awal nnsen, siwa mi nnan: ""a Mass nne$! Semmeê a$ ibekkaven nne$, akked tugut nne$ di lameô nne$. Tebbet isurifen nne$, Sserbeê ane$ $ef ugdud ijehliyen""."
  3,148,"Ifka yasen Öebbi akafi n ddunit, akked ukafi lâali n laxert. Öebbi Iêemmel lâuûam."
  3,149,"A wid iumnen! Ma tu$em awal i wid ijehlen, a kwen rren ar deffir, a ppu$alem txesôem."
  3,150,"Xaîi! Öebbi d Bab nnwen. Neppa, Yif akw imâiwnen."
  3,151,"A Nessekcem tugdi deg ulawen n wid ijehlen, imi curken i Öebbi, ayen iwumi ur d irs ara udabu. Axxam nnsen d times. A yir tanezdu$t i imednas!"
  3,152,"Ni$ Issawel awen Öebbi tidep, di lemâahda S, mi ten tesnegrem, s tsriê iS. Armi, mi tfeclem, temnamarem f lameô, taâûam mbaâd ma Issken awen d ayen têemmlem. Garawen wid ib$an ddunit, garawen wid ib$an laxert. Sinna, Issebâad ikwen fellasen, iwakken a kwen Ijeôôeb. Ni$ Isemmeê awen. Öebbi d Bab n lfevl i lmumnin."
  3,153,"Mi tulim ur d tezzim, u Nnbi inecced ikwen ar ineggura nnwen. Ineûûef awen a$ilif s wayev, iwakken ur t$webnem $ef wayen i wen iôuêen, akked wayen ikwen iu$en. Öebbi Iéôa ayen txeddmem."
  3,154,"Sinna, deffir u$ilif, Issers awen d laman, ives id i$lin $ef urbaâ segwen. Ni$ arbaâ pêebbiôen $ef yiman nnsen, nnwan, $ef Öebbi, ayen ur nelli d tidep, nnwaya n at war tussna. Qqaôen: ""day illa wayen i $ iaânan, di lameô""? Ini: ""s tidep, lameô akw i Öebbi"". Teffren, deg iman nnsen, ayen ur ak mmalen. Qqaôen: ""lemmer illi wayen i $ iaânan, di lameô, ur nepwan$a dagi"". Ini: ""xas ma tellam deg ixxamen nnwen, wid i$ef tura tmen$iwt, a ten tawev s imîeôêen nnsen. Iwakken ad Ijeôôeb Öebbi i illan deg idmaren nnwen, ad Izzizdeg i illan deg ulawen nnwen. Öebbi Iéôa i illan deg idmaren."
  3,155,"Ih, wid segwen iwexxôen asmi mlalent trebbuyaâ, d Cciîan kan iten iccacven, ilmend n kra n wayen kesben. Ni$ Isemmeê asen Öebbi. Akka, Öebbi Ipsemmiê, Iêellem."
  3,156,"A wid iumnen! Ur ppilit am wid ijehlen. Nnan i watmaten nnsen iunagen di tmurt, ne$ ipna$en: ""lemmer llin $uône$, ur mmuten, ur twan$an"". Ad Irr Öebbi, ayagi, d aneggaf deg ulawen nnsen! Öebbi Issidir, Ineqq. Öebbi Ipwali ayen txeddmem."
  3,157,"Ma tepwan$am deg ubrid n Öebbi, ne$ temmutem, ssmaê n Öebbi akked uêunu, war ccekk, ifen ayen la jemâan."
  3,158,"Ma temmutem ne$ tepwan$am, war ccekk, ar Öebbi ara tepwafesrem."
  3,159,"S uêunu n Öebbi, têelmev $uôsen. Lemmer tqeûêev, tes$aôev ul ik, ad baâden fellak. Semmeê asen, ssuter ad ppusemmêen, ciweô iten $ef lameô. Mi tseyyiv, ppkel $ef Öebbi. Ih, Öebbi Iêemmel wid ippkalen."
  3,160,"Ma Iâiwen ikwen Öebbi, ur kwen irennu yiwen. Ma Iooa kwen, anwa illan a kwen iâiwen, deffir eS? £ef Öebbi ara ppeklen lmumnin."
  3,161,"Ur issefk ara i nnbi ad idnes. Win idensen, a d ias s wayen idnes, ass n tnekra. Sinna, yal wa, ad as ippunefk wayen ikseb. Nitni, ur ten pmeôôiôen."
  3,162,"Day win iddan d llza n Öebbi am win isebebben urrif n Öebbi, u tanezdu$t is d Loahennama? A taggara tucmip!"
  3,163,"Ur aâdilen ar Öebbi. Öebbi Ipwali acu xeddmen."
  3,164,"Ni$ Öebbi I$at lmumnin, mi sen d Iuzen Amazan segsen, immal asen issekniyen iS, izzizdig iten, isseêfav asen Tazmamt akked ûûwab, ulamma llan, zik, di ttelfan n ûûeê."
  3,165,"Ma tu$em tiyta, ni$ terram p berdayen. Tennam: ""ansi waya""? Ini: ""aya seg iman nnwen"". Öebbi, s tidep, Izmer i yal cci."
  3,166,"Ayen ikwen iwwten, ass n temlilit n trebbuyaâ, s tsriê n Öebbi. Iwakken ad Iéeô anwi ay d lmumnin,"
  3,167,"u ad Iéeô anwi ay d ixabiten. Nnan asen: ""yyaw, nna$et deg ubrid n Öebbi, ne$ éedmet"". Nnan: ""lemmer nessin a nenna$, yili nedda n yidwen"". Assen, nitni, ar tijehli, ne$ $eô liman, ay qeôben kteô. Qqaren, s yimawen nnsen, ayen ur nelli deg ulawen nnsen. Öebbi Yif akw akken Iéôa ayen teffren."
  3,168,"Wid innan i watmaten nnsen, u nitni qqimen: ""lemmer i $ ssemêessen, ur pwan$en"". Ini: ""sdarit iman nnwen si tmeppant, ma tessawalem tidep ""."
  3,169,"Ur p$ili mmuten wid ipwan$an deg ubrid n Öebbi. Xaîi, d imuddiren. Ad ppuôeéqen ar Mass nnsen."
  3,170,"Ad feôêen s wayen i sen Ifka Öebbi, si lfevl iS. Zhan, imi wid deffir sen, mazal ur ten id nelêiq, ur ppagawaden, ur $weblen."
  3,171,"Zhan s l$it n Öebbi, akked lfevl. Öebbi ur Iveggiâ arraz n lmumnin;"
  3,172,"wid id ijawben i Öebbi akked Umazan, mbaâd ma sâaddan lêif. Arraz ameqwôaêan i wid, segsen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, u êezzben;"
  3,173,"wid iwumi nnan medden: ""ni$ mlalen fellawen imdanen, ihi, agwadet pen"". D$a isnerna liman nnsen, nnan: ""Iqadd a$ Öebbi, Awkil Amxallef""."
  3,174,"U$alen d s l$it n Öebbi akked lfevl, ur ten innul cceôô; ddan d llza n Öebbi. Öebbi d Bab n lfevl ameqwôaêan."
  3,175,"Akka kan ay d Cciîan. Issagwad s imeddukwal is. Ur ten ppagwadet, agwadet iyI, ma d lmumnin ay tellam."
  3,176,"Ur k $webbnen wid ip$awalen ar tijehli. Nitni, s tidep, ur vvuôôen Öebbi, s wacemma. Ib$a Öebbi ur asen Iteg amur di laxert. Fellasen aâaqeb aqeôêan."
  3,177,"Ih, wid iu$en tijehli s liman, ur vvuôôen Öebbi s wacemma. Fellasen aâaqeb aqeôêan."
  3,178,"Ur êeppben wid ijehlen, ar telha yasen, lmudda i sen Nefka. Nefka yasen kan lmudda, iwakken ad rnun ibekkaven. Fellasen aâaqeb isdullun."
  3,179,"Ur illi di leb$i n Öebbi, ad Ioo lmumnin di liêala nnwen, alamma Ifrez axabit seg umâin. Ur illi di leb$i n Öebbi, ad awen Imel tabavnit. Maca, Iferren Öebbi wid i S ihwan, d imazanen iS. Ihi, amnet s Öebbi akked imazanen iS. Ma tumnem, u têezzbem, a ppawim arraz ameqwôaêan."
  3,180,"Ur êeppben wid ipcuêêun deg wayen i sen Ifka Öebbi, si lfevl iS, ard lxiô nnsen. Xaîi, d cceôô nnsen. Ayen cuêêen a ten iarez seg umgaôv, ass n tnekra. I Öebbi, lweôt n tmurt akked igenwan. Öebbi Iéôa ayen txeddmem."
  3,181,"Ni$ Isla Öebbi i wawal n wid innan: ""s tidep, Öebbi d igellil, nekwni d isâayen"". A Naru ayen nnan, akked wayen n$an n lambiyya, war ssebba. Ad asen Nini: ""jeôôbet aâaqeb ujajiê""."
  3,182,"Ayagi, ilmend n wayen xedmen ifassen nnwen. Öebbi ur Ipdennis imdanen."
  3,183,"Wid innan: ""Ih, Öebbi Iâahed a$ ur neppamen s Umazan, alamma issenâat a$ d asfel, ara teçç tmes"". Ini: ""ni$ usan kwen id imazanen, uqbel iw, s ubeggen, akw s wayen d tennam. Ihi, acimi i ten ten$am, ma tessawalem tidep""?"
  3,184,"Ma skaddben k, ni$ skaddben imazanen, uqbel ik, usan d s ubeggen, Ihellilen, akked Tezmamt timnewweôt."
  3,185,"Yal iman ad ijeôôeb tameppant. Ass n tnekra, ad awen ippunefk, kan, warraz nnwen. Win isellken si tmes, ikecmen Loennet, ni$ irbeê. Tameddurt, di ddunit, d zzhu kan ip$uôôun."
  3,186,"A ppeppujeôôbem deg wayla nnwen akked yiman nnwen. Ad wwten aîas degwen, wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt, uqbel nnwen, akked imcurak. Ma tûebôem u têezzbem, ayagi, s tidep, d ayen isselêayen lumuô."
  3,187,"Mi Iîîef Öebbi laâqed n wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt: ""a p tbeggnem i medden, ur p teppeffrem"". Rran p deffir izugar nnsen, u$en yis, ayen irxisen. I icmet wayen u$en!"
  3,188,"Ur p$ili ad sellken, seg uâaqeb, wid ifeôêen s wayen fkan, u b$an a ten ccekôen $ef wayen ur xdimen. Fellasen aâaqeb aqeôêan."
  3,189,"N Öebbi tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan. Öebbi Izmer i yal cci."
  3,190,"Ih, di lxelq n tmurt akked igenwan, akked umgirred n yiv akked wass, d issekniyen i uâqilen;"
  3,191,"Wid id ismektayen Öebbi s ibeddi, s i$imi, s tuééla. Pmeyyizen lxelq n tmurt akked igenwan. A Mass nne$! Ur Texliqev aya d aêerfi. Gedha s yiseK! Sellek a$ seg uâaqeb n tmes."
  3,192,"A Mass nne$! Ni$, s tidep, Keçç, Texziv win Teskecmev ar tmes. Ur llin wid ara isellken imednas."
  3,193,"A Mass nne$! S tidep, nesla i uneccad, la inecced ar liman: ""amnet s Mass nnwen""! Numen. A Mass nne$! Semmeê a$ ibekkaven nne$, Kkes ane$ tucmitin nne$, Ssiwev a$, ar ssmaê iK, akked wid zeddigen."
  3,194,"A Mass nne$! Efk ane$ ayen i a$ Tâahdev s imazanen iK; ur a$ Xezzu ass n tnekra. Keçç, s tidep, ur Tzeglev lemâahda."
  3,195,"Irra yasen Mass nnsen: ""Nek ur Veggiâe$ igi n win, segwen, issewqamen, d ddkeô ne$ d nnta. Wa ikka d seg wa. Wid iunagen, u ssuff$en ten seg ixxamen nnsen, iâatben deg ubrid iW, innu$en, ipwan$an, war ccekk, ad asen Kkse$ tucmitin nnsen, a ten Skecme$ ar leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen"". D akafi s$uô Öebbi. Öebbi, $uôeS akafi amxallef."
  3,196,"Ur k ipqelliq lexdaâ n wid ijehlen di temdint."
  3,197,"Cwiî n zzhu, sinna, axxam nnsen d Loahennama. A yir usu!"
  3,198,"Maca, i wid iêezzben i Mass nnsen: leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, degsen ad wekkôen, d inebgawen n Öebbi. U d wayen illan ar Öebbi, d amxallef i izedganen."
  3,199,"Ih, seg wAt Tezmamt, wid iumnen s Öebbi, s wayen akw i wen ed irsen, akked s wayen i sen d irsen. Unzen i Öebbi, ur u$en ara s issekniyen n Öebbi, ayen ôxisen. I widak, arraz s$uô Mass nnsen. Ni$ Öebbi Ip$awal deg uqeîîi."
  3,200,"A wid iumnen! Üebôet, aznet ûûbeô, begset, êezzbet i Öebbi, amar a prebêem."
